01.02.2020本文字数：1170，阅读时长大约2分钟导读：数百万甚至更高的订单量退改，瞬时10倍电话进线量，13小时极限加班值等数字，或许会铭刻于旅游业者2020年的春节记忆中。
2008-09-04 - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 10: 10, 13 hour limit, and so on, may be engraved in the travel industry's memory of the Spring Festival 2020.
作者 | 第一财经乐琰根据此前携程、途牛、同程等平台发布的节前数据估测，原本2020春节或将有4.5亿人次出游，其中日本是出境游热门目的地。
Sharon's pre-season data, released on previous platforms such as Ctrip, Tuoxiu and Sharon Cheng, estimates there may have been 450 million trips to China's 2020 Spring Festival, with Japan being a popular destination.
然而，这个春节假期非常特殊，由于疫情，大部分人选择宅在家过年，而不是外出旅游。
However, this Spring Festival is very special, because of the epidemic, most people choose to stay at home for the New Year, rather than travel.
从小年夜左右开始，携程、途牛、同程、驴妈妈、中青旅、锦江、春秋等旅游企业进入退单高峰期，加之随后旅行社的团队游暂停，更多的退单蜂拥而至，不少旅游企业进入全员皆客服的状况。
From about the small beginning, carrying Cheng, cattle, the same journey, mother donkey, Zhongqing Travel, Jinjiang, Chunqiu tourism enterprises into the peak billing period, and then travel agency team travel suspension, more return tickets flocked to many tourism enterprises into the full customer service status.
不少企业对第一财经记者表示，本次春节假期的退单量是平日的10倍。
Many enterprises to the first financial reporter said that this spring festival holiday return volume is 10 times the usual.
根据携程1月31日晚间发布的“春运退订大数据”显示，疫情发生以来，截至1月30日，携程客服收到的退改量为数百万单春节旅游订单，客户全球跟团、半自助和定制游的订单损失负担至2月29日前。
According to the "big data" released by Ctrip on the night of January 31, Ctrip had received millions of refunds as of Jan. 30 and lost orders for global follow-up, semi-self-service and custom-made tours until Feb. 29, according to the data released by Ctrip on the night of Jan.
在旅游度假方面，携程对2月29日前全球团队游、半自助、定制游订单免费退订。
On vacation, Ctrip is offering free refunds for global team travel, semi-self-help and custom-made travel orders until Feb. 29.
5天内，携程已基本完成以上全部退订工作。
Within 5 days, Ctrip has basically completed all of the above cancellation work.
虽然目前由于银行和保险端的延迟，部分消费者未收到退费。
Although the bank and the insurance end of the delay, some consumers did not receive a refund.
酒店方面，携程于1月23日公布全球140万家酒店“安心取消保障”计划，国内90%、海外60%酒店已加入。
On January 23, Ctrip announced plans to lift guarantee for 1.4 million hotels around the world, adding 90% of its hotels and 60% of its overseas counterparts.
目前，携程已完成保障范围内全球酒店订单退订。
At present, Ctrip has completed the global hotel orders within the scope of guarantee cancellation.
由于订单量巨大，1月23日峰值期间，进线量增长8倍，IM峰值增长12倍，很多客服经历了13小时极限班次。
Because of the volume of orders, intake increased eightfold during the peak period of January 23, IM peaks increased 12-fold, and many customer services experienced a 13-hour limit.
机票方面，携程多次积极主动沟通全球航司政策，目前境内航空公司已经100%配置完成，境外航空公司的规则已在加急上线。
On air tickets, Ctrip has been proactive in communicating with the global shipping policy, domestic airlines have been 100% complete configuration, the rules of overseas airlines have been accelerated on line.
截至1月30日，平台收到的退改诉求总量达数百万个，相较日常增长近10倍。
As at 30 January, the Platform had received millions of requests for resignations, a nearly tenfold increase over the daily average.
其中除夕当天迎来退改最高峰，百万级的退改诉求涌来平台。
Among them, New Year's Eve ushered in the highest rectification peak, million-level appeals to the platform.
火车票方面，携程接到60万通咨询，单日业务量同比增长了300%，相比平日增长500%，一天内接到近10万通咨询。
On the train ticket side, Ctrip received 600,000 consultation, one-day business volume increased by 300% year-on-year, compared with the usual 500% growth, within a day received nearly 100,000 inquiries.
一些此前选择线下取票的用户，按照铁路要求只能去车站退票，疫情之下，用户不愿去人员密集场所，携程甚至帮一些客人承担起“人肉”退票工作。
Some users who had previously chosen to take tickets offline could only return tickets to the station in accordance with railway requirements. Under the epidemic, users were reluctant to go to densely populated areas.
第一财经记者了解到，同程、途牛、驴妈妈、飞猪等旅游企业也已经基本完成大部分的春节旅游退单，还有小部分退单依然在处理中，目前具体数据还在统计过程中，但根据携程已有数据来看，光携程一家的春节旅游退单已达数百万单，整个行业的数据应该远高于此。
First financial reporter learned that the same trip, cattle, donkey mother, pig and other tourism enterprises have also basically completed the majority of Spring Festival travel returns, a small number of return is still in the process of statistics, but according to Ctrip data, the Ctrip family has millions of returns, the industry data should be much better.
数百万甚至更高的订单量退改，瞬时10倍电话进线量，13小时极限加班值等数字，或许会铭刻于旅游业者2020年的春节记忆中。
Millions or more of these orders will be rescinded, 10 times the number of incoming calls and the 13-hour limit on overtime, perhaps engraved in the travel industry's memory of the Spring Festival 2020.
“国内游的退单还是相对比较简单，但是出境游会涉及到海外的酒店、景点和当地的地接费用等，因此在费用上不一定都能100%全部退给旅行社，但是考虑到游客的心情，所以旅行社几乎是是先行垫付了费用，尽量给游客100%退款。
"Return tickets for domestic tours are relatively simple, but outbound trips involve hotels, attractions and local charges, so they don't always pay 100% back to the travel agent, but considering the mood of the visitor, the travel agency almost always pays in advance, trying to give 100% refund to the visitor.
”一位旅游业者这样告诉第一财经记者。
One tour operator told the first financial reporter.
为了更好地保障退单和退款的处理，携程、同程、途牛、飞猪等旅游企业均启动了数亿元的危机应急保障金来应对。
In order to better protect the return and refund processing, Ctrip, the same route, cattle, hogs and other tourism enterprises have launched hundreds of millions of yuan of crisis emergency funds to respond.
